&lt;h3 id=&quot;looking-forward&quot;&gt;Looking forward&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I set myself the goal to write a blog post every week for the next few months, either on a book I am reading, or on the various topics I’m interested in.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I am looking forward to writting some more posts and I hope my readers will like it&lt;/em&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
